{"title":"Storck Aernario.3 Disc ultralight carbon limited signature edition road bike adds disc brakes!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/24/storck-aernario-3-disc-ultralight-carbon-limited-signature-edition-road-bike-adds-disc-brakes/","date":1632505735000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><img width=\"800\" height=\"573\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134138/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_angled-800x573.jpg\" alt=\"Storck Aernario 3 Signature Disc limited edition ultralight carbon all-rounder lightweight road bike\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134138/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_angled-800x573.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134138/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_angled-297x213.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134138/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_angled-120x86.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134138/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_angled-768x550.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134138/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_angled-1536x1101.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134138/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_angled-2048x1468.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-272618\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>On top of recent new <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/05/storck-aerfast4-aero-road-bike-pushes-uci-limits-plus-new-fascenario4-more/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Aerfast &amp; Fascenario</a> aero road bikes, Storck now updates an ultralight Aernario.3 Disc Signature all-rounder road bike in a super limited edition. The big story though, is that this appears to be the first-ever ultralight Aernario to get disc brakes. And its frame seems to be just as light as ever, building up into a truly lightweight climber’s road bike…</p><h2>Storck Aernario.3 Disc Signature Ltd. ultralight carbon road bike</h2><div id=\"attachment_272697\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134132/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_Markus-Storck.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-272697\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134132/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_Markus-Storck.jpg\" alt=\"Storck Aernario 3 Signature Disc limited edition ultralight carbon all-rounder lightweight road bike,&nbsp;Markus Storck\" width=\"1600\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134132/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_Markus-Storck.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134132/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_Markus-Storck-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134132/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_Markus-Storck-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134132/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_Markus-Storck-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134132/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_Markus-Storck-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134132/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_Markus-Storck-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-272697\">c. Storck</p></div><p>The Aernario has long been Markus Storck’s favorite light road bike, with special editions over the years weighing <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2014/01/20/storck-50th-anniversary-aernario-signature-gets-dream-spec-sub-5-4kg-weight/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">as little as 5.4kg</a> complete with rim brakes. But this seems to finally be the first Aernario to get disc brakes, and the frame seems to be just as light as ever.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134129/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_57-signed-bikes.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134129/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_57-signed-bikes.jpg\" alt=\"Storck Aernario 3 Signature Disc limited edition ultralight carbon all-rounder lightweight road bike,&nbsp;individually signed and numbered\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134129/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_57-signed-bikes.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134129/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_57-signed-bikes-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134129/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_57-signed-bikes-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134129/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_57-signed-bikes-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134129/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_57-signed-bikes-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>On the occasion of the Storck founder’s 57th birthday this past Wednesday, just 57 individually numbered &amp; signed Aernario.3 Disc Signature complete bikes will be sold – in addition to Markus Storck’s #00/57. All bikes are fitted with electronic shift groupsets and hydraulic disc brakes, with fully internal cable routing and complete bike weights from just 6.2kg.</p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134125/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_frame-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134125/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_frame-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Storck Aernario 3 Signature Disc limited edition ultralight carbon all-rounder lightweight road bike,&nbsp;frame\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134125/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_frame-detail.jpg 1800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134125/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_frame-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134125/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_frame-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134125/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_frame-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134125/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_frame-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134125/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_frame-detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"></a></p><p>The Aernario.3 Disc Signature is a new disc brake only carbon bike made from reinforced UD “Japanese Military Carbon Grade Fiber” to deliver a claimed 700-750g frame – presumably designed in Germany and manufactured in China like previous Aernarios. Finishing is kept to a minimum for the Signature edition with a light matte black paint &amp; low-key bronze graphics.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134122/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_non-driveside.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134122/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_non-driveside.jpg\" alt=\"Storck Aernario 3 Signature Disc limited edition ultralight carbon all-rounder lightweight road bike,&nbsp;non-driveside\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134122/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_non-driveside.jpg 900w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134122/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_non-driveside-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134122/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_non-driveside-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134122/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_non-driveside-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134122/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_non-driveside-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"></a></p><p>Storck also says the new disc brake Aernario.3 bike promises to be stiffer than previous generations, without sacrificing comfort thanks to “Hysteresis Flex” in both the seatstays and seatpost.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134119/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-flat-mount-disc-brakes.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134119/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-flat-mount-disc-brakes.jpg\" alt=\"Storck Aernario 3 Signature Disc limited edition ultralight carbon all-rounder lightweight road bike,&nbsp; disc brakes\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134119/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-flat-mount-disc-brakes.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134119/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-flat-mount-disc-brakes-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134119/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-flat-mount-disc-brakes-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134119/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-flat-mount-disc-brakes-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134119/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-flat-mount-disc-brakes-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>The Aernario.3 features flat mount disc brakes and 12mm thru-axles for the first time.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134117/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_fully-internal-cable-routing-cockpit.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134117/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_fully-internal-cable-routing-cockpit.jpg\" alt=\"Storck Aernario 3 Signature Disc limited edition ultralight carbon all-rounder lightweight road bike,&nbsp;internal routing\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134117/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_fully-internal-cable-routing-cockpit.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134117/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_fully-internal-cable-routing-cockpit-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134117/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_fully-internal-cable-routing-cockpit-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134117/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_fully-internal-cable-routing-cockpit-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134117/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_fully-internal-cable-routing-cockpit-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>It also features a new fully integrated one-piece carbon Storck bar+stem cockpit.</p><p>The new disc brake bike features slightly dropped seatstays, an internal wedge seatpost clamp, presumably a round 27.2mm seatpost, a PressFit BB86 bottom bracket, and a tapered carbon steerer fork.</p><p>(<em>The equally light <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/12/16/storck-builds-lightest-road-bike-into-5-7kg-aernario-2-signature-25th-anniversary-edition/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">rim brake Aernario.2</a> will carry over for roadies looking for an even lighter complete build</em>.)</p><h3>Storck Aernario.3 Disc Signature – Pricing, availability &amp; options</h3><div id=\"attachment_272691\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134114/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-Dura-Ace-Di2-angled.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-272691\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134114/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-Dura-Ace-Di2-angled.jpg\" alt=\"Storck Aernario 3 Signature Disc limited edition ultralight carbon all-rounder lightweight road bike,&nbsp;\" width=\"1274\" height=\"950\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134114/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-Dura-Ace-Di2-angled.jpg 1274w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134114/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-Dura-Ace-Di2-angled-297x221.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134114/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-Dura-Ace-Di2-angled-800x597.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134114/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-Dura-Ace-Di2-angled-120x89.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/24134114/Storck-Aernario-3-Signature-Disc-limited-edition-ultralight-carbon-all-rounder-lightweight-road-bike_new-Dura-Ace-Di2-angled-768x573.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1274px) 100vw, 1274px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-272691\">Storck Aernario 3 Disc Signature Dura-Ace Di2 2×12</p></div><p>Just 57 individual, limited Storck Aernario.3 Disc Signature edition bikes will be made available in one of three complete 2×12-speed bike builds and DT Swiss’ light <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/04/15/lightest-ever-1266g-dt-swiss-mon-chasseral-disc-brake-tubeless-carbon-climbers-road-bike-wheels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PRC 1100 Mon Chasseral</a> tubeless carbon wheels. A new Shimano <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/31/shimano-dura-ace-and-ultegra-deliver-fastest-shifting-ever-with-wireless-12-speed-groups/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ultegra Di2</a> option is the lowest cost of entry at 8500€, or upgrade to <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/31/review-wireless-shimano-dura-ace-shifting-is-blazing-fast-but-brakes-are-just-as-impressive/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">new Dura-Ace Di2</a> for 9500€.</p><p>The most expensive option will be the SRAM <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/02/21/sram-red-etap-axs-wireless-road-bike-group-first-ride-review-actual-weights/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Red eTap AXS</a> build at 9777€, surely quite expensive, but all surprisingly palatable for a limited edition superbike like this.</p><p>All are available to pre-order now, with deliveries anticipated in late November 2021.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.storck-bikes.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Storck-bikes.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"a1735fb880bd466ce3a5b988cdbb18c7d8f80bb520abc54fecca2bad3d16bf55","category":"Cycling"}